# npm package + org pages return HTTP 403 to unauthenticated automated GETs
# (npm anti-bot). The links are real — verified by the publish-typescript
# workflow's smoke install and by the registry JSON endpoint (registry.
# npmjs.org). Whitelisting because lychee otherwise treats anti-bot rejection
# as a broken link.
https://www\.npmjs\.com/.*

# slsa.dev/spec — referenced from docs for SLSA L3 framing. The site
# occasionally times out on GitHub-hosted runners (observed
# 2026-05-19 at 05:23 UTC). The links are real and stable; whitelisting
# transient-timeout-prone external standards URLs.
https://slsa\.dev/.*
